Defines acceptable lighting quality and uniformity.

| Parameter | Description | Allowed Range | Preset Defaults |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `lighting_lower_threshold` | Minimum lighting level | 0.55 to 1.0 | STRICT 0.8, MODERATE 0.7, RELAXED 0.55 |
